{"thag21.1:0.1":"Theragatha 21.1 ","thag21.1:0.2":"Mahanipata ","thag21.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag21.1:0.4":"Vangisattheragatha ","thag21.1:1.1":"“Nikkhantam vata mam santam, ","thag21.1:1.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag21.1:1.3":"Vitakka upadhavanti, ","thag21.1:1.4":"pagabbha kanhato ime. ","thag21.1:2.1":"Uggaputta mahissasa, ","thag21.1:2.2":"sikkhita dalhadhammino; ","thag21.1:2.3":"Samanta parikireyyum, ","thag21.1:2.4":"sahassam apalayinam. ","thag21.1:3.1":"Sacepi ettaka bhiyyo, ","thag21.1:3.2":"agamissanti itthiyo; ","thag21.1:3.3":"Neva mam byadhayissanti, ","thag21.1:3.4":"dhamme samhi patitthito. ","thag21.1:4.1":"Sakkhi hi me sutam etam, ","thag21.1:4.2":"buddhassadiccabandhuno; ","thag21.1:4.3":"Nibbanagamanam maggam, ","thag21.1:4.4":"tattha me nirato mano. ","thag21.1:5.1":"Evance mam viharantam, ","thag21.1:5.2":"papima upagacchasi; ","thag21.1:5.3":"Tatha maccu karissami, ","thag21.1:5.4":"na me maggampi dakkhasi. ","thag21.1:6.1":"Aratinca ratinca pahaya, ","thag21.1:6.2":"Sabbaso gehasitanca vitakkam; ","thag21.1:6.3":"Vanatham na kareyya kuhinci, ","thag21.1:6.4":"Nibbanatho avanatho sa bhikkhu. ","thag21.1:7.1":"Yamidha pathavinca vehasam, ","thag21.1:7.2":"Rupagatam jagatogadham kinci; ","thag21.1:7.3":"Parijiyati sabbamaniccam, ","thag21.1:7.4":"Evam samecca caranti mutatta. ","thag21.1:8.1":"Upadhisu jana gadhitase, ","thag21.1:8.2":"Ditthasute patighe ca mute ca; ","thag21.1:8.3":"Ettha vinodaya chandamanejo, ","thag21.1:8.4":"Yo hettha na limpati muni tamahu. ","thag21.1:9.1":"Atha satthisita savitakka, ","thag21.1:9.2":"Puthujjanataya adhamma nivittha; ","thag21.1:9.3":"Na ca vaggagatassa kuhinci, ","thag21.1:9.4":"No pana dutthullagahi sa bhikkhu. ","thag21.1:10.1":"Dabbo cirarattasamahito, ","thag21.1:10.2":"Akuhako nipako apihalu; ","thag21.1:10.3":"Santam padam ajjhagama muni, ","thag21.1:10.4":"Paticca parinibbuto kankhati kalam. ","thag21.1:11.1":"Manam pajahassu gotama, ","thag21.1:11.2":"Manapathanca jahassu asesam; ","thag21.1:11.3":"Manapathamhi sa mucchito, ","thag21.1:11.4":"Vippatisarihuva cirarattam. ","thag21.1:12.1":"Makkhena makkhita paja, ","thag21.1:12.2":"Manahata nirayam papatanti; ","thag21.1:12.3":"Socanti jana cirarattam, ","thag21.1:12.4":"Manahata nirayam upapanna. ","thag21.1:13.1":"Na hi socati bhikkhu kadaci, ","thag21.1:13.2":"Maggajino samma patipanno; ","thag21.1:13.3":"Kittinca sukhancanubhoti, ","thag21.1:13.4":"Dhammadasoti tamahu tathattam. ","thag21.1:14.1":"Tasma akhilo idha padhanava, ","thag21.1:14.2":"Nivaranani pahaya visuddho; ","thag21.1:14.3":"Mananca pahaya asesam, ","thag21.1:14.4":"Vijjayantakaro samitavi”. ","thag21.1:15.1":"“Kamaragena dayhami, ","thag21.1:15.2":"cittam me paridayhati; ","thag21.1:15.3":"Sadhu nibbapanam bruhi, ","thag21.1:15.4":"anukampaya gotama”. ","thag21.1:16.1":"“Sannaya vipariyesa, ","thag21.1:16.2":"cittam te paridayhati; ","thag21.1:16.3":"Nimittam parivajjehi, ","thag21.1:16.4":"subham ragupasamhitam. (…) ","thag21.1:17.1":"Asubhaya cittam bhavehi, ","thag21.1:17.2":"ekaggam susamahitam; ","thag21.1:17.3":"Sati kayagata tyatthu, ","thag21.1:17.4":"nibbidabahulo bhava. ","thag21.1:18.1":"Animittanca bhavehi, ","thag21.1:18.2":"mananusayamujjaha; ","thag21.1:18.3":"Tato manabhisamaya, ","thag21.1:18.4":"upasanto carissasi”. ","thag21.1:19.1":"“Tameva vacam bhaseyya, ","thag21.1:19.2":"yayattanam na tapaye; ","thag21.1:19.3":"Pare ca na vihimseyya, ","thag21.1:19.4":"sa ve vaca subhasita. ","thag21.1:20.1":"Piyavacameva bhaseyya, ","thag21.1:20.2":"ya vaca patinandita; ","thag21.1:20.3":"Yam anadaya papani, ","thag21.1:20.4":"paresam bhasate piyam. ","thag21.1:21.1":"Saccam ve amata vaca, ","thag21.1:21.2":"esa dhammo sanantano; ","thag21.1:21.3":"Sacce atthe ca dhamme ca, ","thag21.1:21.4":"ahu santo patitthita. ","thag21.1:22.1":"Yam buddho bhasati vacam, ","thag21.1:22.2":"khemam nibbanapattiya; ","thag21.1:22.3":"Dukkhassantakiriyaya, ","thag21.1:22.4":"sa ve vacanamuttama”. ","thag21.1:23.1":"“Gambhirapanno medhavi, ","thag21.1:23.2":"maggamaggassa kovido; ","thag21.1:23.3":"Sariputto mahapanno, ","thag21.1:23.4":"dhammam deseti bhikkhunam. ","thag21.1:24.1":"Sankhittenapi deseti, ","thag21.1:24.2":"vittharenapi bhasati; ","thag21.1:24.3":"Salikayiva nigghoso, ","thag21.1:24.4":"patibhanam udiyyati. ","thag21.1:25.1":"Tassa tam desayantassa, ","thag21.1:25.2":"sunanti madhuram giram; ","thag21.1:25.3":"Sarena rajaniyena, ","thag21.1:25.4":"savaniyena vagguna; ","thag21.1:25.5":"Udaggacitta mudita, ","thag21.1:25.6":"sotam odhenti bhikkhavo”. ","thag21.1:26.1":"“Ajja pannarase visuddhiya, ","thag21.1:26.2":"Bhikkhu pancasata samagata; ","thag21.1:26.3":"Samyojanabandhanacchida, ","thag21.1:26.4":"Anigha khinapunabbhava isi. ","thag21.1:27.1":"Cakkavatti yatha raja, ","thag21.1:27.2":"amaccaparivarito; ","thag21.1:27.3":"Samanta anupariyeti, ","thag21.1:27.4":"sagarantam mahim imam. ","thag21.1:28.1":"Evam vijitasangamam, ","thag21.1:28.2":"satthavaham anuttaram; ","thag21.1:28.3":"Savaka payirupasanti, ","thag21.1:28.4":"tevijja maccuhayino. ","thag21.1:29.1":"Sabbe bhagavato putta, ","thag21.1:29.2":"palapettha na vijjati; ","thag21.1:29.3":"Tanhasallassa hantaram, ","thag21.1:29.4":"vande adiccabandhunam. ","thag21.1:30.1":"Parosahassam bhikkhunam, ","thag21.1:30.2":"sugatam payirupasati; ","thag21.1:30.3":"Desentam virajam dhammam, ","thag21.1:30.4":"nibbanam akutobhayam. ","thag21.1:31.1":"Sunanti dhammam vimalam, ","thag21.1:31.2":"sammasambuddhadesitam; ","thag21.1:31.3":"Sobhati vata sambuddho, ","thag21.1:31.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato. ","thag21.1:32.1":"‘Naganamo’si bhagava, ","thag21.1:32.2":"isinam isisattamo; ","thag21.1:32.3":"Mahameghova hutvana, ","thag21.1:32.4":"savake abhivassasi. ","thag21.1:33.1":"Diva vihara nikkhamma, ","thag21.1:33.2":"satthudassanakamyata; ","thag21.1:33.3":"Savako te mahavira, ","thag21.1:33.4":"pade vandati vangiso”. ","thag21.1:34.1":"“Ummaggapatham marassa, ","thag21.1:34.2":"Abhibhuyya carati pabhijja khilani; ","thag21.1:34.3":"Tam passatha bandhapamuncakaram, ","thag21.1:34.4":"Asitamva bhagaso pavibhajja. ","thag21.1:35.1":"Oghassa hi nitaranattham, ","thag21.1:35.2":"Anekavihitam maggam akkhasi; ","thag21.1:35.3":"Tasminca amate akkhate, ","thag21.1:35.4":"Dhammadasa thita asamhira. ","thag21.1:36.1":"Pajjotakaro ativijjha, ","thag21.1:36.2":"Sabbathitinam atikkamamaddasa; ","thag21.1:36.3":"Natva ca sacchikatva ca, ","thag21.1:36.4":"Aggam so desayi dasaddhanam. ","thag21.1:37.1":"Evam sudesite dhamme, ","thag21.1:37.2":"Ko pamado vijanatam dhammam; ","thag21.1:37.3":"Tasma hi tassa bhagavato sasane, ","thag21.1:37.4":"Appamatto sada namassamanusikkhe”. ","thag21.1:38.1":"“Buddhanubuddho yo thero, ","thag21.1:38.2":"kondanno tibbanikkamo; ","thag21.1:38.3":"Labhi sukhaviharanam, ","thag21.1:38.4":"vivekanam abhinhaso. ","thag21.1:39.1":"Yam savakena pattabbam, ","thag21.1:39.2":"satthu sasanakarina; ","thag21.1:39.3":"Sabbassa tam anuppattam, ","thag21.1:39.4":"appamattassa sikkhato. ","thag21.1:40.1":"Mahanubhavo tevijjo, ","thag21.1:40.2":"cetopariyakovido; ","thag21.1:40.3":"Kondanno buddhadayado, ","thag21.1:40.4":"pade vandati satthuno”. ","thag21.1:41.1":"“Nagassa passe asinam, ","thag21.1:41.2":"munim dukkhassa paragum; ","thag21.1:41.3":"Savaka payirupasanti, ","thag21.1:41.4":"tevijja maccuhayino. ","thag21.1:42.1":"Cetasa anupariyeti, ","thag21.1:42.2":"moggallano mahiddhiko; ","thag21.1:42.3":"Cittam nesam samanvesam, ","thag21.1:42.4":"vippamuttam nirupadhim. ","thag21.1:43.1":"Evam sabbangasampannam, ","thag21.1:43.2":"munim dukkhassa paragum; ","thag21.1:43.3":"Anekakarasampannam, ","thag21.1:43.4":"payirupasanti gotamam”. ","thag21.1:44.1":"“Cando yatha vigatavalahake nabhe, ","thag21.1:44.2":"Virocati vitamalova bhanuma; ","thag21.1:44.3":"Evampi angirasa tvam mahamuni, ","thag21.1:44.4":"Atirocasi yasasa sabbalokam”. ","thag21.1:45.1":"“Kaveyyamatta vicarimha pubbe, ","thag21.1:45.2":"Gama gamam pura puram; ","thag21.1:45.3":"Athaddasama sambuddham, ","thag21.1:45.4":"Sabbadhammana paragum. ","thag21.1:46.1":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","thag21.1:46.2":"muni dukkhassa paragu; ","thag21.1:46.3":"Dhammam sutva pasidimha, ","thag21.1:46.4":"saddha no udapajjatha. ","thag21.1:47.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thag21.1:47.2":"khandhe ayatanani ca; ","thag21.1:47.3":"Dhatuyo ca viditvana, ","thag21.1:47.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thag21.1:48.1":"Bahunam vata atthaya, ","thag21.1:48.2":"uppajjanti tathagata; ","thag21.1:48.3":"Itthinam purisananca, ","thag21.1:48.4":"ye te sasanakaraka. ","thag21.1:49.1":"Tesam kho vata atthaya, ","thag21.1:49.2":"bodhimajjhagama muni; ","thag21.1:49.3":"Bhikkhunam bhikkhuninanca, ","thag21.1:49.4":"ye niramagataddasa. ","thag21.1:50.1":"Sudesita cakkhumata, ","thag21.1:50.2":"buddhenadiccabandhuna; ","thag21.1:50.3":"Cattari ariyasaccani, ","thag21.1:50.4":"anukampaya paninam. ","thag21.1:51.1":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","thag21.1:51.2":"Dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","thag21.1:51.3":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","thag21.1:51.4":"Dukkhupasamagaminam. ","thag21.1:52.1":"Evamete tatha vutta, ","thag21.1:52.2":"dittha me te yatha tatha; ","thag21.1:52.3":"Sadattho me anuppatto, ","thag21.1:52.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag21.1:53.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thag21.1:53.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","thag21.1:53.3":"Suvibhattesu dhammesu, ","thag21.1:53.4":"yam settham tadupagamim. ","thag21.1:54.1":"Abhinnaparamippatto, ","thag21.1:54.2":"sotadhatu visodhita; ","thag21.1:54.3":"Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, ","thag21.1:54.4":"cetopariyakovido”. ","thag21.1:55.1":"“Pucchami sattharamanomapannam, ","thag21.1:55.2":"Dittheva dhamme yo vicikicchanam chetta; ","thag21.1:55.3":"Aggalave kalamakasi bhikkhu, ","thag21.1:55.4":"Nato yasassi abhinibbutatto. ","thag21.1:56.1":"Nigrodhakappo iti tassa namam, ","thag21.1:56.2":"Taya katam bhagava brahmanassa; ","thag21.1:56.3":"So tam namassam acari mutyapekho, ","thag21.1:56.4":"Araddhaviriyo dalhadhammadassi. ","thag21.1:57.1":"Tam savakam sakka mayampi sabbe, ","thag21.1:57.2":"Annatumicchama samantacakkhu; ","thag21.1:57.3":"Samavatthita no savanaya sota, ","thag21.1:57.4":"Tuvam no sattha tvamanuttarosi. ","thag21.1:58.1":"Chinda no vicikiccham bruhi metam, ","thag21.1:58.2":"Parinibbutam vedaya bhuripanna; ","thag21.1:58.3":"Majjheva no bhasa samantacakkhu, ","thag21.1:58.4":"Sakkova devana sahassanetto. ","thag21.1:59.1":"Ye keci gantha idha mohamagga, ","thag21.1:59.2":"Annanapakkha vicikicchathana; ","thag21.1:59.3":"Tathagatam patva na te bhavanti, ","thag21.1:59.4":"Cakkhunhi etam paramam naranam. ","thag21.1:60.1":"No ce hi jatu puriso kilese, ","thag21.1:60.2":"Vato yatha abbhaghanam vihane; ","thag21.1:60.3":"Tamovassa nivuto sabbaloko, ","thag21.1:60.4":"Jotimantopi na pabhaseyyum. ","thag21.1:61.1":"Dhira ca pajjotakara bhavanti, ","thag21.1:61.2":"Tam tam aham vira tatheva manne; ","thag21.1:61.3":"Vipassinam janamupagamimha, ","thag21.1:61.4":"Parisasu no avikarohi kappam. ","thag21.1:62.1":"Khippam giram eraya vaggu vaggum, ","thag21.1:62.2":"Hamsova paggayha sanikam nikuja; ","thag21.1:62.3":"Bindussarena suvikappitena, ","thag21.1:62.4":"Sabbeva te ujjugata sunoma. ","thag21.1:63.1":"Pahinajatimaranam asesam, ","thag21.1:63.2":"Niggayha dhonam vadessami dhammam; ","thag21.1:63.3":"Na kamakaro hi puthujjananam, ","thag21.1:63.4":"Sankheyyakaro ca tathagatanam. ","thag21.1:64.1":"Sampannaveyyakaranam tavedam, ","thag21.1:64.2":"Samujjupannassa samuggahitam; ","thag21.1:64.3":"Ayamanjali pacchimo suppanamito, ","thag21.1:64.4":"Ma mohayi janamanomapanna. ","thag21.1:65.1":"Paroparam ariyadhammam viditva, ","thag21.1:65.2":"Ma mohayi janamanomaviriya; ","thag21.1:65.3":"Varim yatha ghammani ghammatatto, ","thag21.1:65.4":"Vacabhikankhami sutam pavassa. ","thag21.1:66.1":"Yadatthikam brahmacariyam acari, ","thag21.1:66.2":"Kappayano kaccissatam amogham; ","thag21.1:66.3":"Nibbayi so adu saupadiseso, ","thag21.1:66.4":"Yatha vimutto ahu tam sunoma”. ","thag21.1:67.1":"“Acchecchi tanham idha namarupe, ","thag21.1:67.2":"(iti bhagava) ","thag21.1:67.3":"Kanhassa sotam digharattanusayitam; ","thag21.1:67.4":"Atari jatim maranam asesam, ","thag21.1:67.5":"Iccabravi bhagava pancasettho”. ","thag21.1:68.1":"“Esa sutva pasidami, ","thag21.1:68.2":"vaco te isisattama; ","thag21.1:68.3":"Amogham kira me puttham, ","thag21.1:68.4":"na mam vancesi brahmano. ","thag21.1:69.1":"Yatha vadi tatha kari, ","thag21.1:69.2":"ahu buddhassa savako; ","thag21.1:69.3":"Acchecchi maccuno jalam, ","thag21.1:69.4":"tatam mayavino dalham. ","thag21.1:70.1":"Addasa bhagava adim, ","thag21.1:70.2":"upadanassa kappiyo; ","thag21.1:70.3":"Accaga vata kappano, ","thag21.1:70.4":"maccudheyyam suduttaram. ","thag21.1:71.1":"Tam devadevam vandami, ","thag21.1:71.2":"puttam te dvipaduttama; ","thag21.1:71.3":"Anujatam mahaviram, ","thag21.1:71.4":"nagam nagassa orasan”ti. ","thag21.1:71.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma vangiso thero gathayo abhasitthati. ","thag21.1:71.6":"Mahanipato nitthito. ","thag21.1:72.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag21.1:72.1":"Sattatimhi nipatamhi, ","thag21.1:72.2":"vangiso patibhanava; ","thag21.1:72.3":"Ekova thero natthanno, ","thag21.1:72.4":"gathayo ekasattatiti. ","thag21.1:72.5":"Nitthita theragathayo. ","thag21.1:73.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag21.1:73.1":"Sahassam honti ta gatha, ","thag21.1:73.2":"tini satthisatani ca; ","thag21.1:73.3":"Thera ca dve sata satthi, ","thag21.1:73.4":"cattaro ca pakasita. ","thag21.1:74.1":"Sihanadam naditvana, ","thag21.1:74.2":"buddhaputta anasava; ","thag21.1:74.3":"Khemantam papunitvana, ","thag21.1:74.4":"aggikhandhava nibbutati. ","thag21.1:74.5":"Theragathapali nitthita. "}